{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my father lived 20 years in Czechoslovakia, and in doing business traveling, he didn't learn a word of Slovakian and/or Czech-- so only Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he conducted his business in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from that point of view, it wasn't difficult for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So no, we-- actually, it was quite good, because we all spoke very well Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, I never been to a Hungarian school myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our accent was not the same as in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, there's a unique Budapest accent, which we never acquired.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we'd been sort of a country accent, which fitted in beautifully, which it came quite handy to me later in my in my-- in my life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everywhere.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- life like-- like no war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you could go--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you could go wherever you wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, wherever you want if you had the money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you see, there was-- I don't want to really go too much political, because I don't really-- maybe I do not know very well, but there was a ruler at that time, Horthy Miklos, who-- they were allies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hungary was allies to Germany but wasn't occupied by Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you see, they had to comply with a lot of things, not to be occupied.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was sort of a cat and mouse game, and-- but the Jews were reasonably safe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In which is--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, that was the government's line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were Hungarians who were--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarians, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The government now-- but they didn't have to be forced very much to-- [LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was a whole system sort of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it came through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, you know, it-- it came from the Parliament.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
